（dietary factor），並說明它們如何影響鐵的吸收。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5bce608a3eb5", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-02521', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-105-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於乳糖不耐症的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["相較北美白種人，亞洲及非洲人種發生機率通常較高", "相較於牛奶，通常食用發酵乳品（如：優格或優酪乳）之耐受性較佳", "攝食含有乳糖的乳製品時，同時攝食其他類別之食物，也無法緩解乳糖不耐之情形", "相較於牛奶，起司在製造過程通常乳糖會流失，故起司也屬於耐受性較佳的食品"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5bce608a3eb5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a43367a2784c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-02522', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-105-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '為維持健康，每人每日均須維持一定量碳水化合物的攝食，美國RDA即建議成年人每天至少需攝食130 克以上可食碳水化合物，則訂定此一標準的根據是：', '["避免肥胖", "可滿足腦部及中樞神經系統對葡萄糖的需求，避免依賴酮體做為能量來源", "預防糖尿病", "由每日所需總熱量換算而來"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5bce608a3eb5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a43367a2784c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
